  "Description": {
    "Text": "\n    <p>It was discovered that Gentooâ€™s Asterisk ebuild does not properly set\n      permissions on its data directories. This only affects OpenRC systems, as\n      the flaw was exploitable via the init script.\n    </p>\n  "
  },
  "Impact": {
